OL,3,CFoster carer says council owe her
OL,4,Cthousands as IT error affects hundreds
OL,6,FA foster carer from Hampshire says the
OL,7,Fcounty council owe her thousands of
OL,8,Fpounds after an IT fault means she
OL,9,Fhasn't been paid in months.
OL,11,FAn online meeting earlier this month
OL,12,Frevealed over 120 foster carers are in
OL,13,Fthe same position, with their weekly
OL,14,Fpayments backed up since December and
OL,15,Fsome even earlier.
