OL,3,CFoster carer says council owe her
OL,4,Cthousands as IT error affects hundreds
OL,6,FMary Whitmore has been a foster carer
OL,7,Ffor nearly a decade, welcoming
OL,8,Fvulnerable children into her home, but
OL,9,Fa technical fault has left her nearly
OL,10,F#5000 out of pocket with no payments
OL,11,Fsince October and over Christmas.
OL,13,FNormally, foster parents like Mary
OL,14,Freceive a weekly payment for each
OL,15,Fchild in their care which goes towards
OL,16,Ffood, clothes and activities such as
OL,17,Fsports or day trips.
