OL,6,FMary says: "It's been tricky because
OL,7,Fit's been Christmas so people have
OL,8,Fbeen off work and trying to get hold
OL,9,Fof people has been difficult.
OL,11,F"They've obviously been inundated with
OL,12,Femails. Nobody really seems to know
OL,13,Fwhat's going on, so that's very
OL,14,Ffrustrating.
OL,16,F"You just kind of go day to day and
OL,17,Fthen, you know, prioritise what you're
OL,18,Fgoing to spend money on.
