OL,6,F"So whereas you might have gone out
OL,7,Ffor a meal or gone to the cinema with
OL,8,Fthe children, you watch a film at home
OL,9,Fand get some popcorn."
OL,11,FLast month, Hampshire County Council
OL,12,Fchanged to a new computer system,
OL,13,Fcalled MOSAIC, which sends out those
OL,14,Fweekly payments to over 1800 foster
OL,15,Fcarers.
OL,17,FBut an error in the transition meant
OL,18,Fover 300 carers didn't receive their
OL,19,Fpayment.
