OL,6,FCllr Edward Heron, Hampshire County
OL,7,FCouncil, says: "We're very sorry for
OL,8,Fthose foster carers who have
OL,9,Fexperienced difficulties. They really
OL,10,Fare incredibly important to us and
OL,11,Fmore importantly incredibly important
OL,12,Fto the children that they support.
OL,14,F"What we have been doing is making
OL,15,Fcontact with carers and we've got in
OL,16,Fplace emergency payments."
